item.title: People Cant Connect to my server?
item.dc:creator: @Fireskrit Fireskrit
item.description:
@Fireskrit wrote:

One way to get people to log onto your server is to open your “No-IP Duc” while the server is up.

Once people have logged on you can then turn off your No-IP Duc to save some internet speed.
